, CFR, San Pastor track, on 
<taxonomicName box="[264,525,1004,1029]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Lasianthaea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="51" pageNumber="52" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="fruticosa">
